1
00:01:37,959 --> 00:01:38,680
Sorry.

2
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:39,640
Sorry, sorry.

3
00:01:48,359 --> 00:01:49,760
Director Zhou is so young.

4
00:01:50,079 --> 00:01:50,599
Yes.

5
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:52,959
Let's take the report

6
00:01:53,280 --> 00:01:54,519
and get another opinion at Third Hospital.

7
00:01:54,959 --> 00:01:55,319
Okay.

8
00:01:59,159 --> 00:01:59,680
Director Zhou.

9
00:02:00,439 --> 00:02:01,560
Can we talk?

10
00:02:06,519 --> 00:02:07,400
Let's go to my office.

11
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:16,960
Leave it open.

12
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:23,479
Director Zhou.

13
00:02:24,120 --> 00:02:25,520
I heard you want me replaced.

14
00:02:25,719 --> 00:02:26,680
Is there some misunderstanding?

15
00:02:27,080 --> 00:02:27,639
There is no misunderstanding.

16
00:02:29,080 --> 00:02:30,000
I just don't see the need

17
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:30,360
to work with someone

18
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:31,560
who can't keep her word.

19
00:02:33,039 --> 00:02:34,599
Then there must be a misunderstanding.

20
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:36,199
Let's clear things up.

21
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:38,439
You broke our agreement.

22
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:40,439
You went to see Liang Mei.

23
00:02:43,120 --> 00:02:43,960
I ran into her by chance.

24
00:02:45,439 --> 00:02:46,159
What a coincidence.

25
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:48,240
Last time, you happened to get

26
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:49,120
the patient's information.

27
00:02:49,479 --> 00:02:50,199
This time, you happened

28
00:02:50,199 --> 00:02:51,280
to run into his family.

29
00:02:51,599 --> 00:02:52,479
Did you also happen

30
00:02:52,520 --> 00:02:54,080
to push her toward an LVAD?

31
00:02:54,879 --> 00:02:56,039
Push her toward what?

32
00:02:56,599 --> 00:02:57,919
I really did happen to see

33
00:02:57,919 --> 00:02:58,800
Lu Dadong's relatives

34
00:02:58,800 --> 00:02:59,639
giving her a hard time,

35
00:02:59,639 --> 00:03:00,520
so I helped her out.

36
00:03:00,759 --> 00:03:01,759
Then she kept asking me

37
00:03:01,759 --> 00:03:02,199
about ECMO

38
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:03,479
and how it differs from an LVAD.

39
00:03:03,599 --> 00:03:04,719
I only answered her questions.

40
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:05,639
That's all.

41
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:07,479
Yes, I did explain

42
00:03:07,479 --> 00:03:08,000
the benefits of an LVAD

43
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:09,759
for end-stage patients.

44
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:11,000
But I also stressed

45
00:03:11,199 --> 00:03:12,759
that she absolutely had to follow the doctors' advice,

46
00:03:12,879 --> 00:03:14,080
because they know

47
00:03:14,080 --> 00:03:14,680
Lu Dadong's condition best.

48
00:03:14,919 --> 00:03:16,080
I did not steer her in any way.

49
00:03:16,560 --> 00:03:17,120
Have you forgotten

50
00:03:17,199 --> 00:03:18,280
your professional role?

51
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:19,159
As a sales representative,

52
00:03:19,319 --> 00:03:20,000
you have no right

53
00:03:20,080 --> 00:03:21,319
to give a patient's family clinical advice.

54
00:03:21,759 --> 00:03:22,800
That wasn't clinical advice.

55
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:23,400
First,

56
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:24,800
I didn't distort the facts.

57
00:03:25,039 --> 00:03:26,120
Second, I didn't steer her unfairly.

58
00:03:26,439 --> 00:03:27,000
I only gave her

59
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:28,039
an objective explanation.

60
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,439
It may be objective to you.

61
00:03:29,759 --> 00:03:30,360
To Liang Mei,

62
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:31,319
it was moral pressure.

63
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:32,360
The moment you told her

64
00:03:32,439 --> 00:03:33,400
an LVAD had greater benefits,

65
00:03:33,560 --> 00:03:34,199
what else could she think?

66
00:03:34,719 --> 00:03:35,479
If there was any possible way,

67
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:36,759
she would feel she had to choose the LVAD.

68
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:38,039
If my answer

69
00:03:38,039 --> 00:03:38,800
changed her mind,

70
00:03:38,960 --> 00:03:39,639
that only means

71
00:03:39,639 --> 00:03:40,560
her priority from the start

72
00:03:40,560 --> 00:03:41,560
wasn't saving money.

73
00:03:41,759 --> 00:03:42,840
It was getting Lu Dadong

74
00:03:42,919 --> 00:03:43,800
the best possible treatment.

75
00:03:43,840 --> 00:03:44,639
That isn't your judgment to make.

76
00:03:44,639 --> 00:03:46,360
To a patient's family, as long as he survives,

77
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:47,280
they'll spend whatever it takes,

78
00:03:47,400 --> 00:03:48,879
even if it bankrupts them.

79
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:50,680
No one needs to pressure her.

80
00:03:50,759 --> 00:03:52,080
You crossed the line. Do you understand?

81
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:00,360
Where did you go?

82
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:01,439
You didn't answer your phone.

83
00:04:05,479 --> 00:04:06,680
Professor Gao said

84
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:07,919
you never went to see him.

85
00:04:08,879 --> 00:04:09,919
I never agreed

86
00:04:09,919 --> 00:04:10,680
to go see him.

87
00:04:11,360 --> 00:04:12,080
Why not?

88
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:12,719
Didn't you really want

89
00:04:12,719 --> 00:04:13,800
to study under him?

90
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:21,079
I did.

91
00:04:21,439 --> 00:04:21,920
But I want him

92
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:23,240
to accept Zhou Xiaofeng,

93
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:25,240
not someone's son.

94
00:04:28,439 --> 00:04:29,319
You found out.

95
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:32,879
Aunt Fang is very kind.

96
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,160
She cares about you

97
00:04:34,279 --> 00:04:35,399
and kept asking how you were.

98
00:04:35,959 --> 00:04:37,279
When I said Professor Gao

99
00:04:37,319 --> 00:04:38,000
would need a recommendation letter,

100
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:39,000
she agreed immediately.

101
00:04:39,439 --> 00:04:40,839
She even said she'd visit him in person.

102
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:42,279
You're her own son.

103
00:04:42,519 --> 00:04:43,120
Professor Gao

104
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:44,439
would surely do her that favor.

105
00:04:50,160 --> 00:04:51,439
Blood is thicker than water.

106
00:04:51,439 --> 00:04:53,160
What mother and son can't reconcile?

107
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:54,720
I think Aunt Fang

108
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:55,560
really wants

109
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:56,639
to repair her relationship with you.

110
00:04:57,079 --> 00:04:57,959
And honestly,

111
00:04:57,959 --> 00:04:58,759
she seems like a good person.

112
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:00,279
She even said that in two years,

113
00:05:00,279 --> 00:05:01,720
if I need a recommendation for my PhD...

114
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:02,959
Do you not understand?

115
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:04,920
How many times have I told you?

116
00:05:05,079 --> 00:05:06,000
I don't want to benefit from her.

117
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:07,199
You have

118
00:05:07,279 --> 00:05:08,040
such a valuable connection in Aunt Fang.

119
00:05:08,079 --> 00:05:08,959
Why not use it?

120
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:10,720
Just because your parents divorced?

121
00:05:11,120 --> 00:05:12,519
She's still your biological mother.

122
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:13,319
So what?

123
00:05:14,079 --> 00:05:15,480
The moment she abandoned me,

124
00:05:15,959 --> 00:05:16,800
I made up my mind

125
00:05:16,879 --> 00:05:18,279
never to rely on her again.

126
00:05:18,279 --> 00:05:19,279
Do you have to go this far?

127
00:05:19,639 --> 00:05:20,839
This concerns your future,

128
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:22,079
yet you're still acting superior

129
00:05:22,079 --> 00:05:22,839
and pretending to be noble.

130
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:35,959
That's my bottom line.

131
00:05:37,759 --> 00:05:38,480
You crossed it.

132
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:45,360
I know

133
00:05:45,519 --> 00:05:46,399
you have a problem with me.

134
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:47,879
You think because I'm in sales,

135
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:48,600
everything I do

136
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:49,639
has an ulterior motive.

137
00:05:49,839 --> 00:05:50,480
But this time,

138
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,519
you truly misunderstood me.

139
00:05:51,759 --> 00:05:52,920
We really did run into each other by chance.

140
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:53,680
I was only trying to help.

141
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:54,560
You had no motive?

142
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:55,680
You approached me and Director Sheng

143
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:56,360
to sell your products.

144
00:05:56,519 --> 00:05:57,759
You even dared approach my patient.

145
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:58,800
And you had no motive?

146
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:00,759
Contacting you and Director Sheng

147
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,279
is part of my job.

148
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:03,120
What's wrong with that?

149
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:03,720
Nothing.

150
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:04,920
But I won't give you another chance

151
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:05,759
to approach my patients.

152
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:07,399
Manager Ouyang,

153
00:06:07,639 --> 00:06:08,279
from today on,

154
00:06:08,519 --> 00:06:09,759
you are no longer welcome in Dongli Cardiology.

155
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:12,959
Do you enjoy

156
00:06:12,959 --> 00:06:14,279
having the power of life and death, Director Zhou?

157
00:06:14,680 --> 00:06:16,000
Does that arrogance feel good?

158
00:06:16,079 --> 00:06:17,360
You brought this on yourself.

159
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:19,079
From then until now,

160
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:20,279
your position has never been sincere.

161
00:06:20,519 --> 00:06:21,560
You're always after something.

162
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:22,879
As long as it benefits you,

163
00:06:23,079 --> 00:06:23,879
anyone can become

164
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:24,639
a stepping stone.

165
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:25,439
And what about you?

166
00:06:25,639 --> 00:06:26,279
You were the one

167
00:06:26,319 --> 00:06:27,720
who wanted distance from Professor Fang.

168
00:06:27,959 --> 00:06:28,399
And now?

169
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:29,879
You're climbing up over your own mother.

170
00:06:30,079 --> 00:06:31,360
How righteous of you to sacrifice family.

171
00:06:31,639 --> 00:06:32,920
When it comes to tactics,

172
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:33,920
I can't compare with you, can I?

173
00:06:57,319 --> 00:06:58,120
Hello, Director Zhou.

174
00:06:59,279 --> 00:07:00,600
I'm Shen Yaqin from Nursing.

175
00:07:02,839 --> 00:07:03,399
Head Nurse Shen.

176
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:04,199
You're back.

177
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:05,560
Could I have two minutes?

178
00:07:06,079 --> 00:07:07,199
Come in. Have a seat.

179
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:13,319
I got back yesterday

180
00:07:13,519 --> 00:07:14,839
and returned to work today.

181
00:07:15,240 --> 00:07:16,199
I wanted to come by

182
00:07:16,279 --> 00:07:17,000
and say hello first.

183
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:19,279
Would you like something to drink?

184
00:07:19,639 --> 00:07:20,240
No need.

185
00:07:25,680 --> 00:07:26,959
I've been looking forward to meeting you.

186
00:07:27,199 --> 00:07:28,279
Did the training go smoothly?

187
00:07:28,439 --> 00:07:28,800
More or less.

188
00:07:29,319 --> 00:07:29,920
I came here

189
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:31,360
to apologize first.

190
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:33,800
I've already reprimanded my brother severely.

191
00:07:34,399 --> 00:07:35,160
Some time ago,

192
00:07:35,199 --> 00:07:36,480
he messaged me,

193
00:07:36,519 --> 00:07:37,319
but I ignored him.

194
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:38,399
I didn't expect

195
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:39,560
that while I was away,

196
00:07:39,879 --> 00:07:41,000
he would come to your clinic

197
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:42,040
and demand an extra appointment.

198
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:43,519
I was examined at the district TCM hospital.

199
00:07:43,639 --> 00:07:44,240
I have the report.

200
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:45,199
Director Zhou.

201
00:07:45,839 --> 00:07:46,720
Could you squeeze me in?

202
00:07:47,439 --> 00:07:48,439
Didn't they tell you outside?

203
00:07:48,439 --> 00:07:49,800
Director Zhou can't add any more patients today.

204
00:07:50,680 --> 00:07:51,199
Director Zhou.

205
00:07:52,279 --> 00:07:53,199
Please just take a look.

206
00:07:53,879 --> 00:07:54,319
I'm sorry.

207
00:07:54,600 --> 00:07:55,279
We truly can't add anyone.

208
00:07:57,319 --> 00:07:58,240
Head Nurse Shen

209
00:07:58,600 --> 00:08:00,360
already spoke to all of you, right?

210
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:01,399
I'm her brother.

211
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:03,160
She's my own sister.

212
00:08:04,279 --> 00:08:04,759
Director Zhou,

213
00:08:05,079 --> 00:08:06,079
just see me first.

214
00:08:06,839 --> 00:08:07,959
You're related to the head nurse,

215
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:08,879
so you can cut the line?

216
00:08:09,279 --> 00:08:10,399
This is my appointment.

217
00:08:10,399 --> 00:08:11,279
You have to wait your turn.

218
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:11,920
Exactly.

219
00:08:11,920 --> 00:08:13,199
How can you cut in line?

220
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:14,399
What are you talking about? Who's cutting?

221
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:15,879
The bearded man is cutting.

222
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:16,439
Exactly.

223
00:08:16,439 --> 00:08:17,360
We've all waited over an hour.

224
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:17,720
Over there.

225
00:08:18,160 --> 00:08:19,360
Do you own the hospital?

226
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:20,839
Everyone, please stay calm

227
00:08:20,839 --> 00:08:22,000
and wait for your number.

228
00:08:22,040 --> 00:08:22,319
But why

229
00:08:22,319 --> 00:08:23,160
does he get to cut in?

230
00:08:23,160 --> 00:08:23,680
Exactly.

231
00:08:24,079 --> 00:08:24,439
Come out.

232
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:25,120
Number 12, right?

233
00:08:25,560 --> 00:08:26,240
Give me a moment.

234
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:31,800
Mr. Shen,

235
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:34,440
you do have coronary artery disease.

236
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:36,000
But to confirm the diagnosis,

237
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:37,200
you still need further tests.

238
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:38,639
We really can't add you today.

239
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:39,320
Xiao Guo,

240
00:08:39,639 --> 00:08:40,559
book Mr. Shen

241
00:08:40,559 --> 00:08:41,159
for my clinic the day after tomorrow.

242
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:41,679
Yes, Director.

243
00:08:43,120 --> 00:08:44,279
So you're saying

244
00:08:44,639 --> 00:08:46,240
you won't see me today?

245
00:08:47,759 --> 00:08:48,440
Please go home.

246
00:08:48,879 --> 00:08:49,559
Director Zhou, next time

247
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:50,519
this happens,

248
00:08:50,600 --> 00:08:51,320
just have them removed.

249
00:08:51,679 --> 00:08:52,360
Don't spare their feelings.

250
00:08:52,879 --> 00:08:53,519
I'm someone who

251
00:08:53,879 --> 00:08:55,679
What I hate most

252
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:57,360
is people using my name

253
00:08:58,240 --> 00:08:59,639
to pull strings and seek special treatment.

254
00:08:59,799 --> 00:09:01,240
You little ingrate.

255
00:09:01,399 --> 00:09:02,679
You used your mother's connections

256
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:04,080
to become department director,

257
00:09:04,279 --> 00:09:04,759
and now you think you're somebody?

258
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:06,000
I'm leaving.

259
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:07,279
You were clearly the one

260
00:09:07,519 --> 00:09:08,159
who wanted distance from Professor Fang.

261
00:09:08,320 --> 00:09:09,600
And now?

262
00:09:09,759 --> 00:09:11,200
You're climbing up over your own mother.

263
00:09:12,519 --> 00:09:13,200
How righteous of you to sacrifice family.

264
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:14,720
About Xiaojing and the others

265
00:09:15,519 --> 00:09:16,600
two days ago,

266
00:09:16,840 --> 00:09:18,000
our nurses were at fault.

267
00:09:18,159 --> 00:09:19,279
I've issued an internal criticism

268
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:20,440
and fined them 300 yuan.

269
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:21,519
I'll also report it

270
00:09:21,840 --> 00:09:22,440
to Director Lin

271
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:24,320
in Cardiac Surgery.

272
00:09:24,759 --> 00:09:25,360
Xiaojing and the others

273
00:09:25,360 --> 00:09:26,360
didn't cause

274
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:28,200
any serious consequences.

275
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:28,799
Wouldn't a warning

276
00:09:28,919 --> 00:09:29,799
be enough?

277
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:31,919
There's no need for a fine.

278
00:09:32,519 --> 00:09:33,799
By the time something serious happens, it'll be too late.

279
00:09:34,240 --> 00:09:35,240
Rules have to be enforced.

280
00:09:35,279 --> 00:09:36,240
A minor punishment now

281
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:38,159
will make them remember.

282
00:09:38,399 --> 00:09:38,720
I'll handle this.

283
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:39,879
Director Zhou,

284
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:41,200
you don't need to worry about it.

285
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:42,240
All right.

286
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:43,440
We'll do it your way.

287
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:44,320
Have some water.

288
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:45,679
There's one more thing.

289
00:09:45,879 --> 00:09:47,120
I heard you're planning

290
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:47,960
continued support for Guizhou,

291
00:09:48,240 --> 00:09:49,360
including sending staff and expertise.

292
00:09:49,480 --> 00:09:49,840
Yes.

293
00:09:50,679 --> 00:09:51,519
I was waiting for you to return

294
00:09:51,519 --> 00:09:52,519
so we could discuss it.

295
00:09:53,159 --> 00:09:54,080
Since you said discuss,

296
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:55,279
I'll be direct.

297
00:09:56,919 --> 00:09:58,480
I oppose sending nurses.

298
00:09:59,080 --> 00:10:00,799
The support program is certainly worthwhile,

299
00:10:01,159 --> 00:10:02,600
but I have to consider reality.

300
00:10:02,879 --> 00:10:03,519
Director Zhou,

301
00:10:03,519 --> 00:10:04,919
you may not understand

302
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:06,559
the daily workload in Nursing.

303
00:10:07,480 --> 00:10:08,799
We're already understaffed.

304
00:10:09,159 --> 00:10:10,120
Almost everyone is working

305
00:10:10,120 --> 00:10:10,799
at full capacity,

306
00:10:11,039 --> 00:10:12,440
or even beyond capacity.

307
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:14,080
We simply cannot spare people

308
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:14,960
for other duties.

309
00:10:20,799 --> 00:10:22,039
I understand your position.

310
00:10:22,759 --> 00:10:23,600
Let's set it aside for now.

311
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:24,840
I'll think it over.

312
00:10:25,360 --> 00:10:26,120
Thank you for considering it.

313
00:10:26,440 --> 00:10:27,279
I'll leave if there's nothing else.

314
00:10:27,720 --> 00:10:28,120
Thank you.

315
00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:29,279
You're back.

316
00:11:29,600 --> 00:11:30,159
You're back.

317
00:11:30,279 --> 00:11:30,840
You're back.

318
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:32,120
There's congee in the kitchen.

319
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:32,720
I'll heat some up.

320
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:33,519
No need, Mom.

321
00:11:33,759 --> 00:11:34,320
I'm not hungry.

322
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:35,320
Dad,

323
00:11:35,720 --> 00:11:36,679
do we still have cold medicine?

324
00:11:37,080 --> 00:11:38,360
I sweated a lot today

325
00:11:38,360 --> 00:11:39,039
and caught a chill.

326
00:11:39,240 --> 00:11:40,720
I'm afraid I'll pass it to Senlin.

327
00:11:41,039 --> 00:11:42,000
Could you make me a dose?

328
00:11:42,639 --> 00:11:43,399
I'll get it.

329
00:14:10,360 --> 00:14:11,080
Why are you here?

330
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:12,360
Why are the lights off?

331
00:14:14,080 --> 00:14:15,480
Lu Dadong is stable.

332
00:14:15,600 --> 00:14:16,960
Lin Yi and Xiaorui aren't home.

333
00:14:17,159 --> 00:14:18,679
Mom is lost in the scenery

334
00:14:18,759 --> 00:14:19,279
and ignoring me,

335
00:14:19,600 --> 00:14:20,960
so I had to seek refuge with my brother.

336
00:14:24,799 --> 00:14:26,840
Instant noodles? Seafood flavor?

337
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:28,000
A double threat.

338
00:14:28,480 --> 00:14:29,840
Your hives are flaring up.

339
00:14:29,879 --> 00:14:31,600
You can't eat seafood or other trigger foods.

340
00:14:31,600 --> 00:14:32,200
Don't you know

341
00:14:32,759 --> 00:14:34,279
seafood flavor

342
00:14:34,600 --> 00:14:35,480
isn't the same as actual seafood?

343
00:14:35,559 --> 00:14:36,440
No.

344
00:14:37,320 --> 00:14:38,440
Good thing I came prepared.

345
00:14:39,480 --> 00:14:40,559
Let's have pizza together.

346
00:14:42,120 --> 00:14:43,080
Did you apply your medicine?

347
00:14:44,639 --> 00:14:45,480
I just ran out.

348
00:14:47,159 --> 00:14:48,679
Perfect timing.

349
00:14:51,759 --> 00:14:52,360
I'll apply it for you.

350
00:14:53,679 --> 00:14:54,799
Are you Doraemon?

351
00:14:56,080 --> 00:14:57,799
Ever since you became department director,

352
00:14:57,960 --> 00:14:59,879
you've been working nonstop

353
00:15:00,559 --> 00:15:01,440
and forgetting to eat or sleep.

354
00:15:01,480 --> 00:15:02,440
You need to take care

355
00:15:16,679 --> 00:15:17,240
of your own health too.

356
00:15:19,320 --> 00:15:20,799
Xiaoran,

357
00:15:22,360 --> 00:15:22,879
am I too idealistic?

358
00:15:24,279 --> 00:15:25,200
What happened?

359
00:15:25,960 --> 00:15:26,879
I told you.

360
00:15:28,200 --> 00:15:29,799
In Guizhou,

361
00:15:30,360 --> 00:15:31,200
I truly felt

362
00:15:32,080 --> 00:15:33,639
that as a leader,

363
00:15:35,519 --> 00:15:36,320
I could help more patients.

364
00:15:37,720 --> 00:15:38,480
I thought

365
00:15:39,799 --> 00:15:40,759
that after returning to Dongli

366
00:15:42,600 --> 00:15:44,320
and becoming department director,

367
00:15:45,480 --> 00:15:46,480
I could accomplish real things

368
00:15:49,360 --> 00:15:50,799
and make reforms.

369
00:15:58,879 --> 00:16:00,039
But I can't move anything forward.

370
00:16:00,399 --> 00:16:01,399
And I've managed

371
00:16:02,840 --> 00:16:03,799
to offend plenty of people.

372
00:16:05,720 --> 00:16:06,600
Who did you offend?

373
00:16:11,360 --> 00:16:13,039
What happened?

374
00:16:14,840 --> 00:16:16,080
Is there anything I can do for you?

375
00:16:16,840 --> 00:16:18,080
You've already done enough.

376
00:16:18,080 --> 00:16:18,639
Just take good care of yourselves.

377
00:16:19,639 --> 00:16:20,399
Besides,

378
00:16:20,799 --> 00:16:22,919
Lin Yi is good at offending people,

379
00:16:23,399 --> 00:16:25,120
and I'll handle communication.

380
00:16:25,840 --> 00:16:26,679
We can both

381
00:16:26,720 --> 00:16:28,000
charge into battle for you

382
00:16:28,399 --> 00:16:29,879
and always have your back.

383
00:16:36,240 --> 00:16:37,080
Thanks, backup team.

384
00:16:43,639 --> 00:16:44,440
This is pretty good.

385
00:16:44,600 --> 00:16:45,279
What flavor is it?

386
00:16:46,480 --> 00:16:47,639
The one you said was good

387
00:16:47,639 --> 00:16:48,600
in the office last time.

388
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:49,600
I bought it especially.

389
00:16:49,840 --> 00:16:50,440
Is this the one?

390
00:16:52,320 --> 00:16:53,279
I thought it was vegetarian.

391
00:16:53,720 --> 00:16:54,679
It has meat.

392
00:17:01,960 --> 00:17:03,320
We're the vendor.

393
00:17:03,679 --> 00:17:04,559
Do you really need

394
00:17:04,599 --> 00:17:05,440
to argue right and wrong

395
00:17:05,559 --> 00:17:06,559
with the client?

396
00:17:07,200 --> 00:17:09,160
I was angry at the time too.

397
00:17:10,960 --> 00:17:11,720
I drove,

398
00:17:11,759 --> 00:17:13,279
transferred to the subway, then rode a bike,

399
00:17:13,480 --> 00:17:14,759
and arrived completely out of breath.

400
00:17:14,839 --> 00:17:15,799
I finally made it there.

401
00:17:16,039 --> 00:17:17,119
I didn't even catch my breath.

402
00:17:17,200 --> 00:17:17,799
The moment I saw him,

403
00:17:17,839 --> 00:17:18,920
he started interrogating me.

404
00:17:19,160 --> 00:17:20,640
Nothing I said mattered.

405
00:17:20,680 --> 00:17:21,599
He wouldn't listen at all.

406
00:17:22,119 --> 00:17:22,680
Yes,

407
00:17:22,920 --> 00:17:23,920
we're the vendor.

408
00:17:24,480 --> 00:17:25,839
But vendors have dignity too.

409
00:17:26,640 --> 00:17:27,519
Dignity?

410
00:17:28,200 --> 00:17:28,839
How much is that worth?

411
00:17:29,240 --> 00:17:30,160
Can it put food on the table?

412
00:17:31,799 --> 00:17:32,440
Understood.

413
00:17:33,519 --> 00:17:34,799
He's angry right now.

414
00:17:35,359 --> 00:17:36,200
Give him a couple of days

415
00:17:36,319 --> 00:17:37,039
to cool down,

416
00:17:37,160 --> 00:17:38,200
then I'll apologize properly.

417
00:17:38,279 --> 00:17:38,640
All right.

418
00:17:40,279 --> 00:17:41,119
You won't get the chance.

419
00:17:41,680 --> 00:17:43,000
Zhang Zhen called again this morning.

420
00:17:43,160 --> 00:17:44,799
His message was simple: replace you.

421
00:17:45,359 --> 00:17:46,160
Why?

422
00:17:46,559 --> 00:17:47,559
Why should I be replaced?

423
00:17:47,759 --> 00:17:48,440
Why?

424
00:17:48,960 --> 00:17:49,920
Because unless we replace you,

425
00:17:50,079 --> 00:17:51,400
all new requests are suspended.

426
00:17:51,839 --> 00:17:52,400
Enough.

427
00:17:52,400 --> 00:17:53,000
Stop talking.

428
00:17:53,240 --> 00:17:54,160
Starting tomorrow,

429
00:17:54,240 --> 00:17:54,920
Dongli Hospital

430
00:17:55,039 --> 00:17:56,079
goes to Qi Qiang's team.

431
00:17:56,160 --> 00:17:56,839
Hand everything over.

432
00:17:56,960 --> 00:17:57,759
Who does Zhou Xiaofeng think he is?

433
00:17:57,920 --> 00:17:58,559
The emperor?

434
00:17:58,720 --> 00:17:59,359
What right does he have

435
00:17:59,359 --> 00:18:00,640
to decide personnel matters at Mai'anpei?

436
00:18:00,960 --> 00:18:01,559
And you.

437
00:18:02,079 --> 00:18:03,599
I worked so hard

438
00:18:03,599 --> 00:18:04,400
to win Dongli.

439
00:18:04,839 --> 00:18:06,119
Now you're casting me aside.

440
00:18:06,519 --> 00:18:07,440
What's with that attitude?

441
00:18:07,759 --> 00:18:08,680
How is this casting you aside?

442
00:18:09,160 --> 00:18:09,400
Yes,

443
00:18:09,440 --> 00:18:10,240
you won Dongli Cardiology.

444
00:18:10,240 --> 00:18:11,039
That's true.

445
00:18:11,039 --> 00:18:11,599
But the same person who made it can ruin it.

446
00:18:11,759 --> 00:18:13,319
Zhou Xiaofeng

447
00:18:13,559 --> 00:18:14,160
made his demand very clear.

448
00:18:14,160 --> 00:18:15,000
Who else can you blame?

449
00:18:15,279 --> 00:18:15,880
No.

450
00:18:16,160 --> 00:18:16,559
No.

451
00:18:16,839 --> 00:18:17,400
I don't agree.

452
00:18:17,519 --> 00:18:18,160
If you don't,

453
00:18:18,400 --> 00:18:19,279
find another job.

454
00:18:19,519 --> 00:18:19,799
Fine.

455
00:18:20,079 --> 00:18:21,279
Then I'll file for labor arbitration.

456
00:18:21,599 --> 00:18:22,000
Go ahead.

457
00:19:05,720 --> 00:19:06,319
Mom.

458
00:19:06,359 --> 00:19:07,480
Grandma said tomorrow

459
00:19:07,480 --> 00:19:08,920
I'm going to fight a monster.

460
00:19:09,240 --> 00:19:11,119
Are my weapons ready?

461
00:19:22,920 --> 00:19:23,880
Don't worry, Senlin.

462
00:19:24,240 --> 00:19:25,519
Mom has everything ready.

463
00:19:25,960 --> 00:19:26,799
Don't be scared.

464
00:20:07,640 --> 00:20:08,240
Mr. Qin,

465
00:20:09,319 --> 00:20:10,200
I was wrong just now.

466
00:20:10,480 --> 00:20:11,160
Please don't be angry.

467
00:20:11,960 --> 00:20:13,039
Give me one more chance,

468
00:20:13,319 --> 00:20:13,960
okay?

469
00:20:15,720 --> 00:20:17,119
Weren't you going to file for arbitration?

470
00:20:17,880 --> 00:20:18,640
You know me.

471
00:20:18,720 --> 00:20:19,440
My mouth moves faster than my brain.

472
00:20:19,960 --> 00:20:22,119
I never think before I speak.

473
00:20:22,920 --> 00:20:24,079
Please don't stay angry.

474
00:20:24,079 --> 00:20:25,200
Help me think of a solution too.

475
00:20:26,000 --> 00:20:26,960
Now you know you were wrong?

476
00:20:27,559 --> 00:20:28,119
Why didn't you lower your head

477
00:20:28,119 --> 00:20:29,160
and soften your tone with the client?

478
00:20:29,279 --> 00:20:30,000
I will. I will.

479
00:20:30,440 --> 00:20:31,000
I will.

480
00:20:31,480 --> 00:20:32,079
Right now, I'd gladly

481
00:20:32,160 --> 00:20:33,319
slide to my knees in a full circle

482
00:20:33,319 --> 00:20:34,319
straight to the client.

483
00:20:34,720 --> 00:20:35,720
But would that help?

484
00:20:36,839 --> 00:20:38,039
I'm just a minor employee.

485
00:20:38,319 --> 00:20:39,400
It doesn't matter if I'm replaced.

486
00:20:39,480 --> 00:20:41,039
But you have to think of the company.

487
00:20:41,279 --> 00:20:42,279
Zhou Xiaofeng says one word,

488
00:20:42,279 --> 00:20:43,279
and you replace me.

489
00:20:43,640 --> 00:20:44,480
What about next time?

490
00:20:44,720 --> 00:20:46,000
Won't he have us completely under his thumb?

491
00:20:48,960 --> 00:20:49,920
I've already had Zhang Zhen

492
00:20:49,960 --> 00:20:50,920
reply to Zhou Xiaofeng.

493
00:20:51,160 --> 00:20:52,319
I can't go back on my word.

494
00:20:53,599 --> 00:20:54,000
Then...

495
00:20:55,000 --> 00:20:55,640
A handover

496
00:20:55,640 --> 00:20:56,680
should have a transition period.

497
00:20:57,400 --> 00:20:58,599
At least a month, right?

498
00:20:59,640 --> 00:21:00,240
Two weeks.

499
00:21:00,920 --> 00:21:01,599
Only two weeks.

500
00:21:01,920 --> 00:21:03,119
I can tell Dongli

501
00:21:03,200 --> 00:21:03,920
these two weeks

502
00:21:03,920 --> 00:21:04,920
are your handover period.

503
00:21:05,160 --> 00:21:06,079
Whether you can turn things around

504
00:21:06,200 --> 00:21:07,079
depends on you.

505
00:21:08,640 --> 00:21:09,039
I can.

506
00:21:09,519 --> 00:21:10,319
Two weeks is enough.

507
00:21:13,240 --> 00:21:14,279
I know

508
00:21:14,279 --> 00:21:15,400
what things are like at home for you.

509
00:21:16,279 --> 00:21:17,680
I kept giving you chances

510
00:21:17,920 --> 00:21:19,160
because I know how hard it is.

511
00:21:21,000 --> 00:21:22,799
Learn from this.

512
00:21:23,960 --> 00:21:25,200
You still think you're a doctor.

513
00:21:26,480 --> 00:21:27,519
In front of doctors,

514
00:21:27,519 --> 00:21:28,759
we're always the weaker party.

515
00:21:29,160 --> 00:21:30,599
And a newly appointed director

516
00:21:31,039 --> 00:21:33,000
is especially sensitive about this.

517
00:21:33,880 --> 00:21:35,160
You bared your teeth at him.

518
00:21:35,559 --> 00:21:36,480
How could you misread the situation so badly?

519
00:21:37,559 --> 00:21:38,759
I really did misread it.

520
00:21:39,599 --> 00:21:40,759
I'll apologize properly

521
00:21:40,880 --> 00:21:41,599
to Director Zhou.

522
00:21:41,920 --> 00:21:43,559
Next time your temper flares,

523
00:21:44,200 --> 00:21:45,839
open your mobile banking app first

524
00:21:45,960 --> 00:21:46,880
and look at your balance.

525
00:21:46,920 --> 00:21:47,880
That should sober you up.

526
00:21:49,039 --> 00:21:50,039
Honestly.

527
00:21:51,079 --> 00:21:52,079
Thank you, Mr. Qin.

528
00:21:54,519 --> 00:21:55,319
Manager Ouyang,

529
00:21:55,559 --> 00:21:56,880
there's truly nothing I can do.

530
00:21:57,640 --> 00:21:58,799
The director was very clear that day.

531
00:21:58,799 --> 00:22:00,000
The first thing I had to do at the hospital

532
00:22:00,079 --> 00:22:01,720
was tell Mr. Qin to replace you.

533
00:22:02,039 --> 00:22:02,640
He said

534
00:22:03,000 --> 00:22:04,000
existing purchases can continue,

535
00:22:04,000 --> 00:22:05,000
but new requests are suspended.

536
00:22:05,480 --> 00:22:06,759
Knowing the director,

537
00:22:07,000 --> 00:22:08,079
there's almost no room

538
00:22:08,279 --> 00:22:09,720
to change his mind.

539
00:22:11,599 --> 00:22:12,839
Still as stubborn as ever.

540
00:22:15,640 --> 00:22:17,240
I'm sorry I dragged you into this.

541
00:22:18,079 --> 00:22:19,200
I'm fine.

542
00:22:19,640 --> 00:22:20,720
But I'm curious.

543
00:22:20,880 --> 00:22:22,400
What exactly did you say that day

544
00:22:22,400 --> 00:22:23,359
to offend him?

545
00:22:24,119 --> 00:22:25,359
He was furious.

546
00:22:26,720 --> 00:22:28,039
How would I dare offend him?

547
00:22:28,400 --> 00:22:29,279
Not just Director Zhou,

548
00:22:29,400 --> 00:22:30,359
Every doctor and nurse,

549
00:22:30,359 --> 00:22:31,559
I respect them all.

550
00:22:32,000 --> 00:22:33,480
It truly was a misunderstanding.

551
00:22:33,799 --> 00:22:34,880
I rushed over that day

552
00:22:34,960 --> 00:22:35,720
in a panic

553
00:22:36,240 --> 00:22:37,440
and was a little worked up.

554
00:22:37,440 --> 00:22:38,880
Maybe I didn't choose my words well.

555
00:22:39,279 --> 00:22:40,000
Dr. Zhang,

556
00:22:40,400 --> 00:22:41,680
you're close to Director Zhou.

557
00:22:42,440 --> 00:22:43,599
Help me think of something.

558
00:22:44,960 --> 00:22:46,559
Once he makes a decision,

559
00:22:46,640 --> 00:22:48,640
it's very hard for anyone to change his mind.

560
00:22:51,759 --> 00:22:53,440
But there is one person

561
00:22:53,799 --> 00:22:55,119
he may listen to.

562
00:23:02,519 --> 00:23:03,240
I've checked.

563
00:23:03,839 --> 00:23:04,920
Recently, two of our

564
00:23:05,039 --> 00:23:06,079
valve patients

565
00:23:06,200 --> 00:23:06,680
and one ECMO patient

566
00:23:06,680 --> 00:23:07,400
used supplies

567
00:23:07,400 --> 00:23:08,359
from your company.

568
00:23:08,920 --> 00:23:10,279
I can print the data for you.

569
00:23:10,559 --> 00:23:12,119
But I still have to remove

570
00:23:12,359 --> 00:23:13,200
the patients' private information

571
00:23:13,240 --> 00:23:14,160
in line with privacy requirements.

572
00:23:14,559 --> 00:23:15,599
I'll redact that information.

573
00:23:16,319 --> 00:23:16,680
Of course.

574
00:23:17,400 --> 00:23:17,839
Also,

575
00:23:18,119 --> 00:23:18,599
you need to sign

576
00:23:18,680 --> 00:23:19,680
this privacy protection agreement.

577
00:23:19,799 --> 00:23:20,319
Let's go.

578
00:23:20,799 --> 00:23:21,119
Sis,

579
00:23:21,400 --> 00:23:21,880
thank you.

580
00:23:22,559 --> 00:23:23,240
Let's add each other on WeChat.

581
00:23:23,279 --> 00:23:24,240
I'll probably need your help again.

582
00:23:24,480 --> 00:23:25,920
I'll confirm with you in advance

583
00:23:25,920 --> 00:23:27,319
and come when it's convenient.

584
00:23:27,519 --> 00:23:28,799
Sure. No problem.

585
00:23:29,279 --> 00:23:30,200
Next time you come,

586
00:23:30,440 --> 00:23:31,039
submit an application in advance

587
00:23:31,160 --> 00:23:31,880
through the mini program,

588
00:23:32,119 --> 00:23:33,240
just like today.

589
00:23:33,640 --> 00:23:34,400
Our rules are very strict now.

590
00:23:34,599 --> 00:23:35,880
Here. You scan me, or I scan you?

591
00:23:36,119 --> 00:23:37,039
I'll scan you, sis.

592
00:23:37,079 --> 00:23:37,759
Sis,

593
00:23:40,640 --> 00:23:41,039
could I also trouble you

594
00:23:41,279 --> 00:23:42,279
to hand out these milk teas

595
00:23:42,400 --> 00:23:43,240
to everyone?

596
00:23:43,359 --> 00:23:44,400
You don't need to be so polite.

597
00:23:45,359 --> 00:23:46,440
This isn't just politeness.

598
00:23:47,519 --> 00:23:48,720
I know

599
00:23:49,079 --> 00:23:49,519
the general ICU

600
00:23:49,519 --> 00:23:49,960
has the hardest workload.

601
00:23:49,960 --> 00:23:50,880
I keep coming here to trouble you.

602
00:23:51,039 --> 00:23:52,039
Buying everyone some milk tea is only fair.

603
00:23:52,440 --> 00:23:54,039
Here, hold it down.

604
00:23:54,279 --> 00:23:55,559
You even know our little superstition.

605
00:23:57,079 --> 00:23:58,440
A little.

606
00:23:58,519 --> 00:23:59,119
Then thank you for the good omen.

607
00:23:59,400 --> 00:24:00,480
Don't spend money next time.

608
00:24:00,680 --> 00:24:01,799
And next time,

609
00:24:02,720 --> 00:24:03,480
remember to apply in advance.

610
00:24:03,480 --> 00:24:04,799
For some basic data,

611
00:24:05,039 --> 00:24:05,920
I can just send it to you.

612
00:24:06,000 --> 00:24:06,720
Thank you, sis.

613
00:24:06,960 --> 00:24:07,440
Xiaoran, are you off work?

614
00:24:08,440 --> 00:24:09,160
Want some milk tea?

615
00:24:09,880 --> 00:24:10,599
No, thanks.

616
00:24:11,119 --> 00:24:11,880
I just ordered coffee

617
00:24:12,119 --> 00:24:12,839
and I'm going to pick it up.

618
00:24:12,920 --> 00:24:13,640
Okay. Bye.

619
00:24:14,039 --> 00:24:14,559
Bye.

620
00:24:14,640 --> 00:24:15,160
Number 56, latte.

621
00:24:21,920 --> 00:24:22,960
Ready.

622
00:24:23,799 --> 00:24:24,200
Thank you.

623
00:24:26,519 --> 00:24:26,960
You're welcome.

624
00:24:27,000 --> 00:24:27,440
Dr. Fang, what a coincidence.

625
00:24:27,480 --> 00:24:28,759
I saw you

626
00:24:29,119 --> 00:24:30,079
in the ICU just now.

627
00:24:30,079 --> 00:24:30,799
You were busy,

628
00:24:30,839 --> 00:24:31,160
so I didn't interrupt

629
00:24:31,160 --> 00:24:31,839
to say hello.

630
00:24:31,839 --> 00:24:32,519
You are...

631
00:24:33,319 --> 00:24:34,160
Ouyang Da,

632
00:24:34,519 --> 00:24:35,759
sales manager at Mai'anpei.

633
00:24:35,799 --> 00:24:36,400
We met before

634
00:24:36,559 --> 00:24:37,759
during Professor Fang's surgery.

635
00:24:37,759 --> 00:24:39,079
Director Zhou introduced us.

636
00:24:39,279 --> 00:24:40,319
Hello.

637
00:24:42,359 --> 00:24:42,799
You're off work, right?

638
00:24:46,359 --> 00:24:47,160
Could I take

639
00:24:48,440 --> 00:24:49,440
five minutes of your time?

640
00:24:49,440 --> 00:24:50,079
Even three minutes.

641
00:24:51,279 --> 00:24:52,119
Dr. Fang,

642
00:24:53,160 --> 00:24:53,799
I'm really not

643
00:24:54,359 --> 00:24:55,319
what Director Zhou said.

644
00:24:55,400 --> 00:24:56,119
I didn't become obsessed with money

645
00:24:56,200 --> 00:24:56,960
and push Liang Mei

646
00:24:57,240 --> 00:24:58,400
just to make a sale.

647
00:24:58,440 --> 00:24:59,359
I'm impulsive,

648
00:25:00,319 --> 00:25:01,440
and sometimes I speak before I think.

649
00:25:01,720 --> 00:25:03,359
When I saw how helpless Liang Mei was,

650
00:25:03,839 --> 00:25:04,799
I really couldn't stop myself

651
00:25:05,200 --> 00:25:06,000
from answering a few questions.

652
00:25:06,359 --> 00:25:07,519
But I stayed completely objective

653
00:25:07,720 --> 00:25:09,319
and kept stressing

654
00:25:09,799 --> 00:25:11,440
that the doctors

655
00:25:11,720 --> 00:25:12,359
had to make the final decision.

656
00:25:12,440 --> 00:25:13,319
But as

657
00:25:13,359 --> 00:25:14,119
a medical-device representative,

658
00:25:14,920 --> 00:25:15,559
you should know very well

659
00:25:15,599 --> 00:25:16,720
that you cannot casually

660
00:25:16,920 --> 00:25:18,119
contact patients

661
00:25:18,359 --> 00:25:19,480
or their families in private.

662
00:25:19,480 --> 00:25:20,599
Yes.

663
00:25:20,599 --> 00:25:21,359
My conduct was inappropriate.

664
00:25:21,920 --> 00:25:22,319
I understand

665
00:25:22,880 --> 00:25:24,000
why Director Zhou was so angry.

666
00:25:24,519 --> 00:25:25,319
After all,

667
00:25:25,319 --> 00:25:26,319
I used to be a doctor too.

668
00:25:26,960 --> 00:25:27,480
You were a doctor?

669
00:25:27,480 --> 00:25:28,440
I worked in Neurology at Sixth Hospital.

670
00:25:29,519 --> 00:25:30,599
But I resigned a year ago.

671
00:25:31,319 --> 00:25:32,319
That's one of Sixth Hospital's strongest departments.

672
00:25:32,960 --> 00:25:34,640
Why did you leave clinical practice?

673
00:25:35,000 --> 00:25:36,880
It's a long story.

674
00:25:38,400 --> 00:25:39,720
To put it simply,

675
00:25:40,920 --> 00:25:41,799
something happened in my family.

676
00:25:43,599 --> 00:25:44,519
Now I'm the only one

677
00:25:44,839 --> 00:25:46,160
holding everything together.

678
00:25:47,160 --> 00:25:48,559
If I stayed in clinical work,

679
00:25:49,240 --> 00:25:50,359
I wouldn't have time to care for my family.

680
00:25:51,000 --> 00:25:52,480
And financially,

681
00:25:52,680 --> 00:25:53,599
it was also

682
00:25:55,359 --> 00:25:56,400
a serious burden.

683
00:25:56,400 --> 00:25:57,160
I know Director Zhou

684
00:25:59,640 --> 00:26:00,519
hates people

685
00:26:00,640 --> 00:26:01,480
approaching his family.

686
00:26:01,519 --> 00:26:02,319
I wouldn't have come to you

687
00:26:03,400 --> 00:26:04,640
unless I had no other choice.

688
00:26:04,799 --> 00:26:05,759
You know

689
00:26:06,960 --> 00:26:07,319
my relationship with Director Zhou.

690
00:26:07,319 --> 00:26:08,720
It's hardly a secret.

691
00:26:09,839 --> 00:26:11,079
So

692
00:26:13,079 --> 00:26:13,920
you want me

693
00:26:14,799 --> 00:26:16,039
to speak to him for you?

694
00:26:16,200 --> 00:26:17,359
Yes.

695
00:26:18,279 --> 00:26:18,759
If I lose

696
00:26:23,480 --> 00:26:24,200
the Dongli account,

697
00:26:24,359 --> 00:26:25,240
next month

698
00:26:25,319 --> 00:26:25,799
I'll only receive my base salary.

699
00:26:25,799 --> 00:26:27,359
I won't be able

700
00:26:27,960 --> 00:26:29,079
to support my family.

701
00:26:29,079 --> 00:26:30,039
I may not even

702
00:26:31,200 --> 00:26:32,880
be able to keep this job.

703
00:26:33,039 --> 00:26:33,839
I admit I made a mistake.

704
00:26:35,920 --> 00:26:37,799
But I don't think it deserves a death sentence.

705
00:26:38,400 --> 00:26:40,279
I've kept trying to explain

706
00:26:41,240 --> 00:26:42,440
and apologize,

707
00:26:42,480 --> 00:26:43,480
but he won't answer my calls,

708
00:26:43,960 --> 00:26:44,759
reply to my messages,

709
00:26:44,759 --> 00:26:45,680
or give me a single chance.

710
00:26:46,440 --> 00:26:47,799
I'm sorry, Manager Ouyang.

711
00:26:49,319 --> 00:26:50,440
I probably

712
00:26:51,079 --> 00:26:51,880
can't help you with this.

713
00:26:51,960 --> 00:26:52,839
Although Director Zhou and I are siblings,

714
00:26:53,839 --> 00:26:55,599
at the hospital,

715
00:26:55,720 --> 00:26:56,279
we are colleagues first.

716
00:26:56,319 --> 00:26:57,400
I can't interfere

717
00:26:58,119 --> 00:26:59,200
with his work decisions.

718
00:26:59,240 --> 00:26:59,880
We have to keep things professional.

719
00:27:00,279 --> 00:27:01,759
I hope you understand.

720
00:27:02,720 --> 00:27:03,720
I was desperate

721
00:27:05,240 --> 00:27:06,599
and came to bother you

722
00:27:06,720 --> 00:27:07,599
for a few minutes.

723
00:27:07,640 --> 00:27:08,400
It's okay.

724
00:27:09,200 --> 00:27:09,759
Dr. Fang,

725
00:27:12,119 --> 00:27:12,720
I have one more request.

726
00:27:13,279 --> 00:27:14,359
Please give these materials

727
00:27:14,839 --> 00:27:16,279
to Director Zhou.

728
00:27:16,319 --> 00:27:16,960
Could you also help me with something else?

729
00:27:19,640 --> 00:27:21,240
The contact person

730
00:27:22,039 --> 00:27:23,119
for Director Zhou's equipment donations

731
00:27:23,119 --> 00:27:24,000
and support work in Guizhou is Old Liu, right?

732
00:27:24,519 --> 00:27:25,759
Could you give me

733
00:27:26,119 --> 00:27:27,440
his contact information?

734
00:27:27,440 --> 00:27:27,920
Why do you need

735
00:27:28,640 --> 00:27:29,880
Old Liu's contact details?

736
00:27:29,920 --> 00:27:30,440
I promised Director Zhou

737
00:27:31,559 --> 00:27:32,519
I would do certain things.

738
00:27:32,559 --> 00:27:33,200
I want

739
00:27:33,680 --> 00:27:34,480
to keep my word.

740
00:27:34,559 --> 00:27:35,480
I've already spoken

741
00:27:36,160 --> 00:27:37,359
with Mai'anpei's partners.

742
00:27:37,480 --> 00:27:38,880
From now on, free programs

743
00:27:39,119 --> 00:27:40,839
such as training

744
00:27:40,960 --> 00:27:41,799
and departmental seminars

745
00:27:41,880 --> 00:27:42,559
will give priority

746
00:27:42,680 --> 00:27:43,519
to primary hospitals in Guizhou.

747
00:27:43,559 --> 00:27:45,319
This free-training list

748
00:27:45,839 --> 00:27:47,599
was compiled

749
00:27:47,759 --> 00:27:48,480
after I learned

750
00:27:48,519 --> 00:27:49,519
what hospitals in Guizhou need.

751
00:27:49,519 --> 00:27:50,240
If I give it to him now,

752
00:27:50,680 --> 00:27:52,039
he may think

753
00:27:52,400 --> 00:27:53,359
I'm bargaining with him.

754
00:27:53,480 --> 00:27:55,079
Don't worry.

755
00:27:57,079 --> 00:27:57,759
You don't need

756
00:27:58,119 --> 00:27:58,880
to say a word for me.

757
00:27:58,880 --> 00:27:59,880
Just give this

758
00:28:00,039 --> 00:28:00,640
to him.

759
00:28:00,680 --> 00:28:01,519
Whether he uses it is entirely up to him.

760
00:28:01,880 --> 00:28:03,359
I simply don't want

761
00:28:04,000 --> 00:28:04,680
this opportunity to go to waste.

762
00:28:04,720 --> 00:28:05,680
All right.

763
00:28:11,440 --> 00:28:11,839
Thank you.

764
00:28:13,440 --> 00:28:13,920
Also,

765
00:28:14,519 --> 00:28:15,039
if you have any

766
00:28:15,160 --> 00:28:16,119
questions about the products,

767
00:28:16,200 --> 00:28:17,200
you can ask me anytime.

768
00:28:17,480 --> 00:28:18,759
I'll do my job properly

769
00:28:19,759 --> 00:28:21,160
until my last day.

770
00:28:23,079 --> 00:28:24,039
May I add you on WeChat?

771
00:28:24,720 --> 00:28:25,240
Sure.

772
00:28:25,799 --> 00:28:26,359
I'll scan you.

773
00:28:31,680 --> 00:28:32,160
Sorry to bother you.

774
00:28:32,720 --> 00:28:33,160
It's fine.

775
00:28:47,799 --> 00:28:48,279
What's wrong?

776
00:28:49,079 --> 00:28:50,319
There's a squirrel.

777
00:28:50,680 --> 00:28:51,559
A squirrel?

778
00:28:52,039 --> 00:28:53,240
Don't scare it.

779
00:28:57,599 --> 00:28:58,799
It's a red-bellied squirrel.

780
00:28:58,960 --> 00:29:00,799
Its belly is reddish brown.

781
00:29:02,200 --> 00:29:02,680
Senlin,

782
00:29:03,519 --> 00:29:05,119
don't disturb the doctor's work.

783
00:29:06,079 --> 00:29:06,759
It's all right.

784
00:29:07,880 --> 00:29:09,160
My little grandson is very lively.

785
00:29:10,160 --> 00:29:11,160
You're very knowledgeable, little one.

786
00:29:12,480 --> 00:29:12,960
Uncle,

787
00:29:13,440 --> 00:29:13,960
look.

788
00:29:14,880 --> 00:29:16,240
My mom also told me

789
00:29:16,440 --> 00:29:17,279
that squirrels adjust

790
00:29:17,319 --> 00:29:18,559
their routines

791
00:29:18,759 --> 00:29:20,240
according to food availability.

792
00:29:20,599 --> 00:29:21,000
So

793
00:29:21,160 --> 00:29:22,799
some city squirrels

794
00:29:23,039 --> 00:29:23,599
sleep in.

795
00:29:23,839 --> 00:29:25,319
But the squirrels at the hospital

796
00:29:25,519 --> 00:29:26,440
wake up early,

797
00:29:26,599 --> 00:29:27,960
because mornings here

798
00:29:28,079 --> 00:29:29,640
begin at six.

799
00:29:30,200 --> 00:29:31,680
You even know the hospital schedule,

800
00:29:32,640 --> 00:29:33,279
Senlin.

801
00:29:34,920 --> 00:29:35,920
Grandma's calling us.

802
00:29:36,240 --> 00:29:36,920
Bye, doctor.

803
00:29:37,079 --> 00:29:37,599
Bye.

804
00:29:37,640 --> 00:29:38,160
Don't run. Don't run.

805
00:29:38,279 --> 00:29:38,720
You can't run.

806
00:29:39,000 --> 00:29:39,799
I've told you before.

807
00:29:40,000 --> 00:29:40,839
Walk slowly.

808
00:29:41,559 --> 00:29:43,920
One, two, one.

809
00:29:43,960 --> 00:29:44,359
Do you hear me?

810
00:29:44,519 --> 00:29:45,200
Walk slowly.

811
00:29:45,200 --> 00:29:47,000
One, two, one.

812
00:29:47,119 --> 00:29:48,200
Slowly.

813
00:29:48,519 --> 00:29:49,960
Walk slowly.

814
00:29:49,960 --> 00:29:51,759
One, two, one.

815
00:29:52,200 --> 00:29:54,200
One, two, one.

816
00:29:54,960 --> 00:29:55,880
How many times have I told you?

817
00:29:56,000 --> 00:29:56,519
Slow down. Slow down.

818
00:30:00,680 --> 00:30:01,960
We've landed.

819
00:30:02,160 --> 00:30:03,400
You were in such a hurry to see me.

820
00:30:03,519 --> 00:30:05,079
Where are you taking me for a welcome meal?

821
00:30:09,519 --> 00:30:10,319
How about the cafeteria?

822
00:30:13,839 --> 00:30:14,640
I'm fine with that.

823
00:30:16,759 --> 00:30:18,160
Okay, I'll be back soon.

824
00:30:18,599 --> 00:30:19,359
Not the cafeteria.

825
00:30:25,839 --> 00:30:26,279
Hello, Director.

826
00:30:28,359 --> 00:30:29,119
I'm coming right now.

827
00:30:29,200 --> 00:30:29,680
Wait for me.

828
00:30:31,079 --> 00:30:32,200
I lost again.

829
00:30:35,079 --> 00:30:35,359
You...

830
00:30:35,359 --> 00:30:35,839
Dad. Mom.

831
00:30:36,319 --> 00:30:36,880
Mom's here.

832
00:30:37,160 --> 00:30:37,559
Mom.

833
00:30:38,160 --> 00:30:38,960
Slow down. Slow down.

834
00:30:39,559 --> 00:30:40,720
What did Mom tell you?

835
00:30:40,920 --> 00:30:41,839
Slowly.

836
00:30:42,400 --> 00:30:43,119
Take it slow.

837
00:30:43,680 --> 00:30:45,119
Did you defeat the monster, Mom?

838
00:30:45,319 --> 00:30:46,160
Are you taking me

839
00:30:46,200 --> 00:30:47,160
to fight monsters now?

840
00:30:47,799 --> 00:30:49,000
Thank you for waiting for Mom, Senlin.

841
00:30:49,240 --> 00:30:49,920
Let's go.

842
00:30:51,920 --> 00:30:53,880
I just saw a red-bellied squirrel.

843
00:30:54,119 --> 00:30:55,160
A doctor

844
00:30:55,160 --> 00:30:56,559
almost scared it away.

845
00:30:57,440 --> 00:30:58,720
What doctor?

846
00:30:59,319 --> 00:31:02,279
A doctor in a white coat.

847
00:31:03,759 --> 00:31:05,160
I also want braised beef with potatoes,

848
00:31:05,160 --> 00:31:06,160
fish fillets in tomato sauce,

849
00:31:06,279 --> 00:31:06,640
and one more...

850
00:31:06,640 --> 00:31:07,160
Done scanning.

851
00:31:09,640 --> 00:31:10,559
This is no fun.

852
00:31:10,559 --> 00:31:11,240
I came all this way back,

853
00:31:11,319 --> 00:31:12,279
and all I get is cafeteria food.

854
00:31:12,440 --> 00:31:13,799
And I can't even order whatever I want.

855
00:31:14,119 --> 00:31:15,880
Your brother rarely has time to treat you.

856
00:31:15,920 --> 00:31:16,759
Be grateful.

857
00:31:18,440 --> 00:31:19,119
How is Xiaorui?

858
00:31:21,039 --> 00:31:21,720
Professor Xu's team

859
00:31:21,720 --> 00:31:22,720
gave him a lot of encouragement.

860
00:31:22,920 --> 00:31:23,720
The stem-cell therapy

861
00:31:23,720 --> 00:31:24,839
also gave him hope.

862
00:31:25,440 --> 00:31:26,000
Anyway,

863
00:31:26,319 --> 00:31:27,200
at least in Hainan,

864
00:31:27,240 --> 00:31:28,039
he was quite happy.

865
00:31:29,079 --> 00:31:29,839
That's good.

866
00:31:33,519 --> 00:31:35,079
Make sure he gets his follow-up tests on time.

867
00:31:35,359 --> 00:31:35,880
Then we'll decide

868
00:31:35,880 --> 00:31:36,640
whether we need to go there again.

869
00:31:37,400 --> 00:31:38,400
He'd be thrilled.

870
00:31:40,319 --> 00:31:41,640
About that patient with triple-vessel disease,

871
00:31:41,799 --> 00:31:42,640
let's try

872
00:31:42,640 --> 00:31:43,480
to operate this week.

873
00:31:44,200 --> 00:31:44,720
Sure.

874
00:31:45,079 --> 00:31:46,279
I'll send you the OR schedule

875
00:31:46,279 --> 00:31:46,720
when the time comes.

876
00:31:46,920 --> 00:31:47,400
You decide.

877
00:31:57,279 --> 00:31:58,119
What about Lu Dadong?

878
00:31:58,480 --> 00:31:59,319
How is he?

879
00:31:59,640 --> 00:32:00,960
He improved a lot

880
00:32:01,200 --> 00:32:01,920
after going on ECMO.

881
00:32:02,119 --> 00:32:03,039
We may be able to try weaning him off

882
00:32:03,039 --> 00:32:04,279
in four or five days.

883
00:32:04,559 --> 00:32:05,200
That soon?

884
